Package frogger.controllers

Class SceneController

java.lang.Object
frogger.controllers.SceneController
public class SceneController
extends Object

The class SceneController manages the scene in the Frogger game.

Methods in SceneController used to add and remove Level panes and user interface panes as well as switch between them as scenes.
